document_data.mainbody:
piderweb Alley was a small backalley that was located in the city of Waterdeep.
Spiderweb Alley was located in Waterdeeps Dock Ward. The alley branched off of Snail Street, cutting west briefly before terminating at a dead end. Spiderweb Alley was intersected on its north side by Three Daggers Alley and on its south side by Ghemmers Alley.
